<mvc:View controllerName="UI5_course.controller.App" 
    xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns:form="sap.ui.layout.form" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <Page id="pgTask1" title="{i18n>Task1.title}">
        <content>
            <form:SimpleForm editable="true" layout="ResponsiveGridLayout" id="form0">
                <form:content>
                    <core:Title text="{i18n>formTitle}" id="title0"/>
                    <Label text="{i18n>formTxtAuthor}" id="lblAuthor"/>
                    <Input width="50%" id="inAuthor" value="{/Author}" />
                    <Label text="{i18n>formTxtName}" id="lblName"/>
                    <Input width="50%" id="inName" value="{/Name}"/>
                    <Label text="{i18n>formTxtReview}" id="lblReview"/>
                    <Input width="100%" id="inReview" value="{/Review}"/>
                    <Toolbar>
                        <ToolbarSpacer/>
                        <Button id="bnBack1" class="nav_back" icon="sap-icon://navigation-left-arrow" text="{i18n>btnBackText}" type="Emphasized" press="onNavBack"/>
                        <Button icon="sap-icon://action" text="Send" type="Default" press="onSend"/>
                        <ToolbarSpacer/>
                    </Toolbar>
                </form:content>
            </form:SimpleForm>
        </content>
    </Page>
</mvc:View>